PrecisAuthority for the St. John's Port Corporation to carry out a real estate transaction with the City of St. John's which, in summary, provides for the closure of and acquisition by the Port Corporation of a section of a municipal street allowance (Habour Drive) that will be used for the expansion of its Main Terminal, in exchange for the transfer to the City of another piece of land which is to be used for the realignment of another municipal street, namely Steers Cove.
